sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Backend as odh-dashboard Backend<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant BFF as Sidecar BFF<br/>(gen-ai/maas/automl/etc.)
    participant Upstream as Upstream Service<br/>(Pipelines/Registry/LlamaStack)

    Note over Browser,OAuth: Flow 1: User Authentication & Dashboard Access
    Browser->>Route: GET / (HTTPS/443)
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    KRBP-->>Browser: 302 Redirect to OAuth
    Browser->>OAuth: OAuth2 Authorization Code Flow
    OAuth-->>Browser: Bearer Token (cookie/header)
    Browser->>Route: GET / + Bearer Token
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    KRBP->>KRBP: Validate: user can list projects<br/>(SubjectAccessReview)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward + x-forwarded-access-token<br/>+ x-auth-request-user (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>K8sAPI: GET /api/status<br/>Bearer Token (user) HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: User identity + cluster info
    Backend-->>KRBP: JSON response
    KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Browser: Dashboard SPA + config

    Note over Browser,BFF: Flow 2: Frontend Loads Federated Module
    Browser->>Route: GET /_mf/gen-ai/remoteEntry.js
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    KRBP->>Backend: /_mf/* proxy (HTTP/8080)
    Backend->>BFF: Forward to gen-ai sidecar<br/>HTTPS/8143 + x-forwarded-access-token
    BFF-->>Backend: remoteEntry.js + chunks
    Backend-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Browser: Module Federation JS bundle

    Note over Browser,Upstream: Flow 3: BFF Proxies to Upstream Service
    Browser->>Route: POST /api/service/pipelines/runs
    Route->>KRBP: Forward (TLS Reencrypt)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>Upstream: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token (user) HTTPS/8443
    Upstream-->>Backend: Pipeline run response
    Backend-->>KRBP: JSON response (HTTP)
    KRBP-->>Route: HTTPS response
    Route-->>Browser: Pipeline run result

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Kubernetes Watch via WebSocket
    Browser->>Route: WSS /wss/k8s/api/v1/namespaces/ns/pods?watch=true
    Route->>KRBP: WebSocket upgrade (TLS Reencrypt)
    KRBP->>Backend: WS upgrade (localhost/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: WSS Watch request<br/>Bearer Token (base64 subprotocol)<br/>HTTPS/6443
    loop Watch Events
        K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch event (WSS)
        Backend-->>KRBP: Watch event (WS)
        KRBP-->>Route: Watch event (WSS)
        Route-->>Browser: Watch event (WSS)
    end
